item.title: Prayer bpn12996 in Daga
item.description: Endi koewa toborapen apane Maman? Wata ge: Maman wat taragasepen. Me Maman di. Uruga Me nao mega nagirewa amba uruga aeamat Me wani gapan tapen. (Source category: Koewa Toborapen U’uraewa (Assistance)) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 12996)
